The paper discusses methods for automatic text line segmentation in historical documents, which involves image processing, computer vision, and natural language processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.DL (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.LG (Machine Learning and Statistics).
